\section*{STEP 3: IDENTIFY THE MOST COMMON ACLS RHYTHMS}

Normal Sinus Rhythm (NSR)
- Normal P-wave
- Normal QRS Complex
- Normal T-wave
- HR: 60-100 BPM (at rest)
- Treatment: None
