\section*{Sinus Tachycardia}
- Normal P-wave
- Normal QRS Complex
- Normal T-wave
- HR: >100 BPM (at rest)
- Treatment: Reverse underlying condition (fever, anxiety, exercise), beta-blockers (metoprolol, sotalol)
