\section*{1st degree heart block}
- Prolonged PR interval due to delay in AV signal transmission
- P-wave may be buried in the preceding T-wave
- Treatment: Transcutaneous pacing (only indicated if prolongation of the PR interval is $>400 \mathrm{~ms}$ ))
